The following external PHP modules are required:

Module		Version		License		URL
		Tested
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# If you want to extract information from video/audio files and generate
# thumbnails from videos
php-ffmpeg	0.6.3		GPLv2		http://ffmpeg-php.sourceforge.net/


